script = ExtResource("3_fs5il")
barrel_id = 8
barrel_name = "Roulette Lady"
barrel_desc = "[b]Roulette Lady Barrel[/b]
Barrel collected from the Roulette dealer. Grant you ability similar to its owner.

Possible rolls:
[ul]
Newton's Third Law: Knock you back when shoot the nearby environment. Increased damage but decreased firerate.
Protective Barrier: A group of blue shields circle you, grant you damage resistance.
Ball Bullet: Shoot a single huge bouncy ball. Significantly increased damage but reduce firerate and projectile speed.
[/ul]"
